files\n   136\t    Given prd/v1-mvp.md contains Gherkin snippets\n   137\t    Th
en tests/bdd/auth.feature should exist and cover registration/login\n   138\t   
And tests/bdd/profile.feature should exist and cover profile completion\n   139\
t    And tests/bdd/matching.feature should exist and cover swipe/match\n   140\t
   And tests/bdd/im.feature should exist and cover messaging\n   141\t```\n   14
2\t\n   143\t#### 技术要求\n   144\t- API BDD 使用 `jest-cucumber`。\n   145\t- 
`make test` 默认行为包含：单元测试 + BDD 测试。\n   146\t- CI 中 `test` job 必须
跑通 `make test`。\n   147\t\n   148\t---\n   149\t\n   150\t### US-INF-5：代码
质量闸门与 CI Pipeline\n   151\t\n   152\t**作为** 代码维护者，  \n   153\t**我
希望** 每次提交和 PR 都自动执行格式检查、静态分析和文档健康检查，  \n   154\t**
以便** 保持代码风格一致并防止文档与代码脱节。\n   155\t\n   156\t#### 验收标准\n
  157\t> 以上验收标准的完整 Gherkin 用例详见 `tests/bdd/infrastructure_bootstrap
.feature`。\n   158\t\n   159\t```gherkin\n   160\tFeature: Code Quality Gates\n
  161\t  Scenario: Pre-commit hooks run automatically\n   162\t    Given I stage
a TypeScript or Dart file\n   163\t    When I run "git commit"\n   164\t    Then
eslint/dart format should auto-fix formatting issues\n   165\t    And the commit
should be blocked if there are unfixable lint errors\n   166\t\n   167\t  Scenar
io: PR checks enforce docs health\n   168\t    Given a PR is opened\n   169\t   
When the CI pipeline runs\n   170\t    Then "make check-docs" should validate al
l internal markdown links\n   171\t    And "make check-docs" should verify gloss
ary terms are used consistently\n   172\t```\n   173\t\n   174\t#### 技术要求\n 
 175\t- Husky + lint-staged：提交前跑 `eslint --fix`、`prettier --write`、`dart 
format`。\n   176\t- `make check-docs` 实现：\n   177\t  - 使用脚本检查 `docs/` 
和 `prd/` 内部 markdown 链接有效性；\n   178\t  - 校验 `docs/product-specs/gloss
ary.md` 中的业务术语在代码和文档中被一致引用。\n   179\t- CI Pipeline 至少包含：
Install → Lint/Format → Build（API + Mobile）→ Test → Docs Health Check → Contra
ct Sync Check。\n   180\t\n   181\t---\n   182\t\n   183\t### US-INF-6：可观测性
基线\n   184\t\n   185\t**作为** 运维工程师 / 开发者，  \n   186\t**我希望** 系
统运行日志、错误和关键指标可被收集和查询，  \n   187\t**以便** 快速定位线上问题
。\n   188\t\n   189\t#### 验收标准\n   190\t> 以上验收标准的完整 Gherkin 用例详
见 `tests/bdd/infrastructure_bootstrap.feature`。\n   191\t\n   192\t```gherkin\
n   193\tFeature: Observability Baseline\n   194\t  Scenario: API produces struc
tured logs\n   195\t    Given the API is handling requests\n   196\t    When I i
nspect the application logs\n   197\t    Then each log entry should be in JSON f
ormat\n   198\t    And should contain fields: timestamp, level, message, trace_i
d, user_id\n   199\t\n   200\t  Scenario: Error tracking is active\n   201\t    
Given an unhandled exception occurs in the API or Mobile app\n   202\t    Then t
he error should be reported to the configured error tracking service\n   203\t  
 And the report should include the stack trace and environment metadata\n   204\
t```\n   205\t\n   206\t#### 技术要求\n   207\t- API 侧使用 `pino`，统一 JSON 日
志格式。\n   208\t- 接入 Sentry（或等效服务）用于 API 和 Mobile 双端错误追踪。\n
  209\t- 基础指标采集：API QPS、P95 延迟（NestJS 拦截器）、Redis 缓存命中率、Soc
ket.io 连接数。\n   210\t- 日志中必须包含 `trace_id`（通过请求头透传或生成）和 `
user_id`。\n   211\t\n   212\t---\n   213\t\n   214\t### US-INF-7：安全与合规基
线\n   215\t\n   216\t**作为** 平台运营者，  \n   217\t**我希望** 在用户注册、内
容上传和交互环节建立最低限度的安全与合规防护，  \n   218\t**以便** 降低法律风险
并保护用户（尤其是未成年人）。\n   219\t\n   220\t> **⚠️ 风险标注**：本需求涉及未
成年人保护和内容审核，属于敏感合规领域，建议人类确认具体法律要求（如目标市场是否
涉及欧盟 GDPR、中国未成年人保护法）。\n   221\t\n   222\t#### 验收标准\n   223\t
> 以上验收标准的完整 Gherkin 用例详见 `tests/bdd/infrastructure_bootstrap.featur
e`。\n   224\t\n   225\t```gherkin\n   226\tFeature: Security and Compliance Bas
eline\n   227\t  Scenario: Block underage registration\n   228\t    Given a new 
user enters a birth date\n   229\t    When the calculated age is less than 18\n 
 230\t    Then registration should be rejected with code 1000\n   231\t    And n
o user record should be created\n   232\t\n   233\t  Scenario: Content moderatio
n webhook skeleton exists\n   234\t    Given a user uploads a photo to the avata
r endpoint\n   235\t    When the upload completes\n   236\t    Then the system s
hould trigger a content moderation webhook event\n   237\t    And the photo stat
us should default to "pending_review"\n   238\t\n   239\t  Scenario: Block and r
eport tables are ready\n   240\t    Given the database migrations have been appl
ied\n   241\t    Then the "blocks" table should exist with columns: blocker_id, 
blocked_id, reason, created_at\n   242\t    And the "reports" table should exist
with columns: reporter_id, target_id, type, description, status, created_at\n   
243\t```\n   244\t\n   245\t#### 技术要求\n   246\t- 年龄计算：根据 `birth_date`
与当前 UTC 时间精确计算周岁，`< 18` 则阻断注册。\n   247\t- OSS 上传后触发内容审
核 Webhook（MVP 阶段可对接阿里云内容安全或预留空实现）。\n   248\t- `user_photos
` 表须包含 `moderation_status` 枚举字段（`pending_review`、`approved`、`rejected
`）。\n   249\t- `blocks` 和 `reports` 表必须在初始 Migration 中创建；MVP 阶段至
少暴露基础 API（`POST /blocks`、`POST /reports`），前端入口可暂时隐藏。\n   250\
t\n   251\t---\n   252\t\n   253\t## 3. 非功能需求\n   254\t\n   255\t### 性能\n
  256\t- `make dev` 启动完整环境的时间 < 60 秒（P95）。\n   257\t- `make generat
e-types` 单模块生成时间 < 10 秒。\n   258\t- `make db:migrate` 在空数据库上执行
时间 < 30 秒。\n   259\t\n   260\t### 安全\n   261\t- 开发环境的 MySQL 和 Redis 
不暴露于公网（仅 `localhost` 或 Docker 内部网络）。\n   262\t- CI 中不泄露敏感环
境变量（数据库密码、API Key 等）。\n   263\t- 种子数据中的测试用户使用虚拟手机号
，避免误拨真实号码。\n   264\t\n   265\t### 兼容性\n   266\t- 工程脚本支持 macOS
和 Linux。\n   267\t- Windows 开发者可通过 WSL2 或 Docker Desktop 运行 `make dev
